<div
  class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center relative pt-24"
  style="background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: linear-gradient(#e8e8e8 1.5px, transparent 1.5px, transparent calc(100% - 1.5px), #e8e8e8 calc(100% - 1.5px)), linear-gradient(90deg, #e8e8e8 1.5px, transparent 1.5px, transparent calc(100% - 1.5px), #e8e8e8 calc(100% - 1.5px))"
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h1
      class="font-black text-8xl mb-12 text-center relative "
      style="letter-spacing: -4px; z-index: 2;"
    >
      Tailwind component generator for Rails
    </h1>
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full"
    style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.2), rgba(255,255,255,1)); z-index: 1;"
  ></div>
</div>
<div class="max-w-xl mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
  <div class="space-y-8 w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <aside class="bg-black text-white p-6 rounded-lg w-full max-w-lg font-mono">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="flex space-x-2 text-red-500">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500" ></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500" ></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500" ></div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm">bash</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <p class="text-green-400">$ gem install railwind</p>
        <p class="text-white">Successfully installed railwind-0.1.25</p>
        <p class="text-white">1 gem installed</p>
        <p class="text-green-400">$</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
    <%= link_to components_button_path, class: "font-semibold" do %>
      <button
        class="
          bg-yellow-400
          rounded-full
          flex
          items-center
          justify-center
          font-bold
          py-4
          px-12
          text-2xl
          transition
          hover:bg-yellow-500
        "
      >
        View documentation
      </button>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto pb-24">
  <div
    class="mt-24 w-full border shadow shadow-xl bg-white rounded p-6 text-xl"
    style="transform: rotate(-1deg)"
  >
    <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Hey there!</h3>
    <p class="mb-4 leading-8">
      My name is Christian, the dev behind Railwind. I built this tool
      to help Rails developers like you build beautiful, responsive, and
      accessible web applications with Tailwind CSS.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4 leading-8">Funny enough, I'm _mostly_ a JavaScript dev and was heavily influenced
      by
      <a
        href="https://ui.shadcn.com/"
        target="_blank"
        class="font-semibold border-b border-black"
      >shadcn/ui</a>
      .. basically this but for React apps. I'm also super new to Rails and was
      searching for something like shadcn for a side project I'm working on.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4 leading-8">
      Long story short, I couldn't find anything like it and this became my
      first real Rails project.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-6 leading-8">Hope you find it useful! Please feel free to submit any issues or pull
      request.</p>
    <p>Christian</p>
  </div>
</div>
